re not functioning as a unit where the caption *closes* what the card *opened*. The caption should be the kicker, not the echo. Additionally, ''#ChepaукCries'' contains a Cyrillic ''у'' (likely a typo from the source), which will break hashtag discoverability. Hashtag count is 16 (within range), but ''#BuyHomesInChennai'' and ''#RealEstateIndia'' are low-traffic filler tags that dilute the trend-first strategy. The trend hashtag ''#SureshRaina'' is correctly placed first.','{"card_hook_strength": 8.5, "trend_and_shareability": 8.8, "caption_punch": 7.5, "hashtag_strategy": 7.0}','Strong hook leveraging Suresh Raina''s real-time emotional return to Chepauk (IPL 2025 context). Dual-layer nostalgia: cricket legend + homecoming metaphor seamlessly bridges to real estate. Hindi-English mix resonates with Housing.com''s core demographic. Meme format + stadium imagery = high scroll-stop potential. Metaphor ''addresses bhulaye nahi bhulte'' (some addresses never fade) is clever emotional anchor to property ownership. Hashtag density (#SureshRaina trending + #CSK + #IPL2025) ensures discoverability. CTA is soft but clear (link in bio). Weakness: CTA could be more explicit; some users may miss the real estate angle initially (which is intentional but risks lower conversion).','{"hashtag": "#SureshRaina", "volume": "rising", "platform": "instagram", "context": "Suresh Raina''s emotional return to Chepauk to support Dhoni is going viral, with fans calling it the most nostalgic IPL moment in years.", "creative_hook": "Raina left, but Chepauk never left his heart. \ud83e\udd79\ud83d\udc9b Mr. IPL phir aa gaya apne ghar. Because some homes are more than just walls \u2014 they''re your identity. Apna IPL moment find karo Housing.com pe. #SureshRaina #WhistlePodu", "city_hint": "Chennai", "tags": ["cricket", "ipl", "chennai", "sports", "viral", "celebrity"]}','{"media_format": "meme_overlay", "meme_concept": "Use the viral clip/photo of Suresh Raina arriving at Chepauk stands today \u2014 emotional, waving to crowd, in civilian clothes. Overlay text bottom: ''Retire ho gaya. Sheher chhod diya. Phir bhi Chepauk ne bula hi liya. Kuch addresses bhulaye nahi bhulte.''", "card_text": "Retire ho gaya. Sheher chhod diya.\nPhir bhi Chepauk ne bula hi liya. \ud83d\udc9b\nKuch addresses bhulaye nahi bhulte.", "trend_hashtag": "#SureshRaina", "city_hint": "chennai", "city_link": "https://housing.com/in/buy/chennai", "alt_text": "Meme overlay on a warm, golden-toned image of Chepauk stadium with a crowded emotional crowd. Text reads: ''Retire ho gaya. Sheher chhod diya. Phir bhi Chepauk ne bula hi liya. \ud83d\udc9b Kuch addresses bhulaye nahi bhulte.'' Housing.com branding in corner. Evokes nostalgia and homecoming."}','https://pub-f574a876869d4654b354fad0d657b289.r2.dev/housing-marketeer/8c103b6b/instagram_b7e2d9f1_meme_placeholder.png');
