bat mid-swing) OR his calm walk-off after the 2011 World Cup winning six. Overlay text in bold white with yellow accent.", "card_text": "Thala ne 16 saal cool rehke match finish kiya \ud83d\ude81\nTu ek ghar finish nahi kar paaya?", "trend_hashtag": "#ThalaForever", "city_hint": null, "city_link": null, "alt_text": "Meme overlay on a cricket stadium background. Top text reads: ''Thala ne 16 saal cool rehke match finish kiya \ud83d\ude81'' Bottom text reads: ''Tu ek ghar finish nahi kar paaya?'' Housing.com branding and logo visible. Yellow and gold color palette nodding to CSK. Helicopter shot visual motif connecting cricket finishing to closing on a dream home."}','https://pub-f574a876869d4654b354fad0d657b289.r2.dev/housing-marketeer/436bddb1/instagram_a1f2c3d4_meme_placeholder.png');
