 your perfect match on Housing.com \u2014 because great connections change everything. #Melodi #GharKiTalaash", "city_hint": null, "tags": ["viral", "celebrity"]}','{"media_format": "meme_overlay", "meme_concept": "Use the viral Modi-Meloni ''Melodi'' selfie from the G7 summit (the one that broke the internet). Overlay text on top half: ''Melodi ki selfie viral \ud83d\udcf8'' \u2014 Bottom half overlay: ''Aapke naye ghar ki first pic kab?'' with small Housing.com logo bottom-right.", "card_text": "Melodi ki selfie viral, aur aapke naye ghar ki first pic? \ud83d\udcf8\ud83c\udfe1", "trend_hashtag": "#Melodi", "city_hint": null, "city_link": null, "alt_text": "Meme overlay graphic showing the viral Modi-Meloni ''Melodi'' selfie side by side with a joyful family taking a first photo outside their new home, with Hindi text overlay reading: Melodi ki selfie viral, aur aapke naye ghar ki first pic? with Housing.com branding at the bottom"}','https://pub-f574a876869d4654b354fad0d657b289.r2.dev/housing-marketeer/6ce667d0/instagram_a1f2c3d4_meme_placeholder.png');
