lodi energy but make it real estate \ud83e\udd0c\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf3 Just like India-Italy relations, the best investments are built on strong foundations. Kya aapka ghar bhi ek viral moment deserve karta hai? Find your perfect match on Housing.com \u2014 because great connections change everything. #Melodi #GharKiTalaash", "city_hint": null, "tags": ["viral", "celebrity"]}','{"media_format": "meme_overlay", "meme_concept": "Use the viral Modi-Meloni ''Melodi'' selfie from the G7 summit (the one that broke the internet). Overlay text on top half: ''Melodi ki selfie viral \ud83d\udcf8'' \u2014 Bottom half overlay: ''Aapke naye ghar ki first pic kab?'' with small Housing.com logo bottom-right.", "card_text": "Melodi ki selfie viral, aur aapke naye ghar ki first pic? \ud83d\udcf8\ud83c\udfe1", "trend_hashtag": "#Melodi", "city_hint": null, "city_link": null, "alt_text": "Meme overlay image split into two panels: left panel shows the viral Modi-Meloni ''Melodi'' selfie moment; right panel shows a happy couple taking a selfie in front of their new home. Overlay text reads: ''Melodi ki selfie viral, aur aapke naye ghar ki first pic? \ud83d\udcf8\ud83c\udfe1'' with Housing.com branding at the bottom."}','https://pub-f574a876869d4654b354fad0d657b289.r2.dev/housing-marketeer/6ce667d0/instagram_a1f2c3d4_meme_placeholder.png');
